g.text: Sends HTTP request to list the default patient's list
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Sends HTTP request with the token to list the default patient's list
Validates the data and tries to list the patients
Displays initial list and asks for the data to filter the patients
Sends the data to filter the patients
The data can be First Name and/or Last Name and/or Full Name
and/or Date of Birth and/or Gender and/or Medical Record Number
